02:01:04.659 --> 02:01:09.704
To je bilo ime mog brata.
On je tvoj stric.

02:01:12.959 --> 02:01:16.460
U popodnevnim satima
pecali smo crvenrepke.

02:01:23.811 --> 02:01:27.855
